title: Full Show (Dak out 6-8 weeks with injury, Baker Mayfield loses to Browns, Tom Brady shines in win over Cowboys)
description:
00:00 Dak reportedly to miss 6-8 weeks following thumb injury
26:00 Was Baker Mayfield robbed in loss to Browns?
59:42 CeeDee Lamb has 2 receptions for 29 yards in loss to Bucs
1:13:19 Has Tom Brady not lost a step at age 45?
1:24:45 Trey Lance held to 164 yards and 1 INT in loss to Bears
1:32:12 Can Cowboys still win the NFC East this year?
1:41:08 Lamar Jackson passes for 3 TDs in win over the Jets
1:45:58 Patrick Mahomes passes for 360 yds and 5 TDs in win over Cardinals
